quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  7,179,"Ne toto Efwe khwalonjela omulilo kwa Jahannam abaanji mu majini nende abandu. Bali nende emioyo, halali shibachikhonyelanga okhumanya tawe. Ne bali nende tsimoni, halali shibatsilolelanga tawe. Ne bali nende amarwi, halali shibakawulililanga tawe. Abo bali shinga tsisolo, halali abo nabakori muno. Abo nibo abakoyana."
  7,180,"Ne Nyasaye ali nende amera amalayi muno, kho kekhonyele okhumusaba. Ne leshe balia banyasinjia oluyali lwa amera keke. Hambi ano, betsa okhurungwa kalia akabakholanga."
  7,181,"Ne mubalia abakhwaloonga, abandi baliwo balunjisinjia khubwatoto ne khubwo baleng’asinjia."
  7,182,"Ne balia abakatsula ebimanyisio biefu, khulabakhwesa kaala kaala munjila yabalamanyile tawe."
  7,183,"Nasi nditsa okhubahelesia ebise. Toto obututi bwanje nobusiro muno."
  7,184,"Koo, shibaparangakhwo tawe? Owashaabwe oyo abula lilalu tawe. Shali shiosishiosi tawe halali omwikanyilisi owa habulafu."
  7,185,"Koo, shibahengangakhwo obwami bwomwikulu nende mushialo, nende ebindu bia Nyasaye yalonga, mbu awundi indukho yabu ili ahambi tawe? Mana kalali kano, ni makhuwa shina akandi akabalasuubila?"
  7,186,"Aba Nyasaye alekhulanga bakora, abo babula ubalunjisia tawe. Ne abalekha mubukori bwabu nibabeyabeyanga mubuwofu."
  7,187,"Bakhurebanga ebise bieyindukho (eyo) mbu okhurulila khwayo khuliba lina, boola mbu; “Obumanyi bwayo buli khu Nyasaye wanje Omulesi. Abulao umanyile ebise biayo halali Ye mwene. Ni isiro mwikulu nende khushialo. Shilibetsela tawe halali mapwoka." Bakhurebanga opara mbu newe wayikoonya wayimanya. Boola mbu; “Obumanyi bwayo buli khu Nyasaye, halali abandu abanji shibamanyile tawe.""